pageProduct.name: Sambucol Soothing Manuka Honey 16 Lozenges
pageProduct.description:
General Information

Sambucol Soothing Relief Throat Lozenge made with Black Elderberry and Manuka Honey coats the throat.

Sambucol the original Black Elderberry Brand. Blended with great tasting highly concentrated Black Elderberry and the soothing comfort of Manuka Honey. To Coat the throat for relief in winter and times of seasonal changes. 

Size: 16 Pack

Ingredients

Sugar, Glucose (from corn), Elderberry Extract, Flavour Enhancer (Lactic Acid), Natural Flavour, Manuka Honey (2%).

Directions

Take 1 lozenge every 2-3 hours as needed. Maximum 8 lozenges daily.
